<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">panel-stele</rs>, broken below (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.705</measure> x <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.575</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.17</measure>). The relief is of a <rs type="decoration">gladiator</rs> (a retiarius) with very light armour, and bare legs, carrying a short sword in his right hand and advancing right; behind him lies a long implement, perhaps a trident.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on upper moulding.</p>
</div>
